        private void put(Instant time,
                 String url,
                 String id,
                 Path path,
                 TypeToken<?> typeToken)
        puts this "request" in the request cache (all the underlying maps)
        Parameters:
        time - the timestamp
        url - the url
        id - the id, the URL encoded, base 64, SHA-128 hash or the url
        path - the relative path with a filename matching the id
        typeToken - a TypeToken containing the Type of the request

      • put

        public void put(ApiRequest<?> request)
        puts a request in the request cache by its url, id, cachePath, and generic runtime type the id is a URL, base 64 encoded SHA-128 hash of the url hashToBase64(String) the path is the relative directory path and the filename ApiRequest.getRelativeCachePath() the filename is the id with the file extension ApiRequest.getFileExtension() the Type is from ApiRequest.getPojoClass() or ApiRequest.getPojoType()
        Parameters:
        request - a request
